          "reading": "Aruite ikimasu.",
          "meaning": "I go on foot. (walking)"
        }
      ],
      "notes": "で marks the means of transportation. For walking, use あるいて (te-form of aruku) instead.",
      "difficulty": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "g14_02",
      "pattern": "〜に のります / を おります",
      "meaning": "Get on/off transportation",
